headline: Allegion Stock Earns Relative Strength Rating Upgrade
summary: Allegion  stock had its Relative Strength (RS) Rating upgraded from 65 to 72 Wednesday — a welcome improvement, but still short of the 80 or better score you look for.  See if Allegion stock can continue to show renewed price strength and hit that benchmark.  Is Allegion Stock A Buy?
